(Yes, Destructor's ship is KitKat's base.)


::KitKat::
She got the transmission and responded. "I am KitKat, leader of the 
Predacons. Please join us, you will be welcomed here."

She turned to GoldenEye. "Go and find that pod."

GoldenEye nodded and transformed into eagle mode and flew off. 


GoldenEye::
She flew over and found the pod. She landed and transformed into bot 
mode. She nodded to the bot. "I am GoldenEye, sent by KitKat. Follow 
me to the base."

She looked at him a second before turning and walking towards the 
base. She thought he was cute.
